'''Cailin Praytor''' is the name of [[Rachel Greene|Rachel]]'s redheaded nurse in "[[The One Where Rachel Tells...]]" and in "[[The One With Ross' Step Forward]]", portrayed by [[Evie Peck]].

Her name is only seen on her name tag, "Cailin Praytor, R.N. (registered nurse)".
